p: Filed on the 21st day of Oct 1887

I hereby certify that the within recognizance was entered into and acknowledged before me, and the same is herto certified to the Clerk of the District Court for record in accordance with the provisions of Section 1035 of the Code of Washington Territry
Witness my hand this 20th day of october A.D. 1887
W H Bush Sheriff of Chehalis county Wash Tery
